{"title":"我的北山坡","authors":["毕东海"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":4,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的北山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕东海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我回到你身边去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听树叶弹琴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看松鼠攀壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低头就是野花的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸手够着云朵的白衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我回到你身边去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽清风一绺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淋碎雨几滴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用你的酸枣穿珠链"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借你的水洼照镜子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我回到你身边去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送飞鸟上路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎夕阳休憩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟在羊群后翻画书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骑在牛背上吹牧笛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你哺育了我喂养了我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小麦玉米高粱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄豆红薯芝麻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那胖胖大枣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那鲜嫩的瓜果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我蒙昧时代的摇篮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我恩重如山的母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我金黄金黄的北山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我火红火红的北山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我别你很久很久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我离你很远很远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住高楼大厦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"着西装革履"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘宝马奔驰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可我不忘我是你膝下的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走南闯北天涯海角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你而行呀为你而歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我灵魂深处藏有你一抔泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生长着你永远的嘱托"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能想你北山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起你来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的梦就会飘起伤感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的诗就会流下泪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就想插翅飞到你地头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光着脚丫扶起犁耙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去翻耕那种久违的亲切的气息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绚若桃花的北山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静若处子的北山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是棵五彩缤纷的树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我轻轻一摇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有无尽的欢声和笑语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有无尽的思念和乡愁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷落下呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷落下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北山坡我的北山坡"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}